{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Flag or Rage is a physics-based platformer game for up to 8 players!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose and place obstacles and platforms, cooperate with your teammates to reach the top and capture the flag, or cunningly hinder your opponents and survive alone.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>You can't play alone!! I recommend playing with a friend.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Gameplay</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Compete against opponents to choose obstacles or platforms and place them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use various items to step on your teammates and opponents, reach the top, and capture the flag.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As night falls, darkness creeps in. Avoid the darkness and survive alone.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Even after reaching the top or being eliminated, you can still hinder the remaining opponents. Continuously disrupt and seek revenge on your enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Duo Mode (2vs2vs2vs2)</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Cooperate with your teammate and sabotage your opponents.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Squad Mode (4vs4)</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Work closely with your teammates to overcome seemingly impossible terrain and reach the top.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Solo Mode</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Everyone is your enemy. Step on your opponents, reach the top, or survive alone.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Online multiplayer for up to 8 players.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unique and competitive obstacle selection mechanism.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Two victory conditions: reach the top or survive.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Consistent and cohesive graphics.</p></li></ul>","achievements":{"highl